{"word":"προσφέρω","slug":"προσφέρω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>προσφέρω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:πρός\">πρός</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:φέρω\">φέρω</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘cause movement of <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ someth.\">someth.</a> or someone to a <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pers.\">pers.</a> or place’, <b>bring, present<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> of <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pers.\">pers.</a> <b><a href='B:470 4:24'>Mt 4:24</a>; <a href='B:470 8:16'>8:16</a>; <a href='B:470 18:24'>18:24</a>; <a href='B:480 10:13'>Mk 10:13</a>; <a href='B:490 23:14'>Lk 23:14</a>;</b> of cultic self-offering <b><a href='B:650 9:14'>Hb 9:14</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> of things<b><p class=\"pp4\"/>—<pp>α.</pp></b> in general <b><a href='B:470 2:11'>Mt 2:11</a>; <a href='B:470 22:19'>22:19</a>; <a href='B:510 8:18'>Ac 8:18</a>.<p class=\"pp4\"/>—<pp>β.</pp></b> of cultic offering or presentation <b><a href='B:470 5:23'>Mt 5:23f</a>; <a href='B:480 1:44'>Mk 1:44</a>; <a href='B:650 8:3'>Hb 8:3f</a>; <a href='B:650 10:12'>10:12</a>.</b> In imagery <b><a href='B:500 16:2'>J 16:2</a>; <a href='B:650 5:1'>Hb 5:1</a>, <a href='B:650 5:7'>7</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> as <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pass.\">pass.</a>, of one brought close to another but <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> transferred <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ act.\">act.</a> sense of displaying tolerance, <b>bear (with), deal (with) <a href='B:650 12:7'>Hb 12:7</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:προσφάτως\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:προσφιλής\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}